{"tid":1242503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李家超:沒參與警方使用武力決定","createTime":"2019-06-19T05:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T10:06:29.000Z","uid":77196,"like":588,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"5e4584e46370a8e03ac37317ddd2449c82757e9f","tid":1242503,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:35:40.000Z","msg":"民主派議員在立法會大會就金鐘示威衝突中，警方使用武力的問題提出緊急質詢。公民黨郭家麒質詢當日是誰人下令向示威者鎮壓，決定是否中聯辦的命令，以及李家超與特首林鄭月娥事前是否知情。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>李家超回應稱沒有參與，指任何涉及行動的都是由警隊來執行，警隊的最高負責人是警務處處長盧偉聰</strong></span>，又指在巨大壓力下，希望各方互相理解。<br />\n<br />\n郭家麒又追問是否要由盧偉聰一人問責，李家超重申由警隊執行職務，警員有責任令傷害減到最低。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2167466/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2167466%2F&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dWWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=342181aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2167466/</a>"},{"pid":"fe0125713beec8c158a41ab69e8fc8de414f1b9b","tid":1242503,"uid":257422,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:35:49.000Z","msg":"追究 警察濫權濫用武力 先係我地依家既王牌！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242366\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242366</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818f68fbddc653f6ad7fd91e135dcaf9430ee3d0","tid":1242503,"uid":256246,"like":198,"dislike":0,"score":198,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:37:06.000Z","msg":"好囉wor, 毅進唔係好蝦wor, 下下割到咁揾個毅進呀head出嚟頂下好wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d1557483da4b886f250e50b484aa412ec93471","tid":1242503,"uid":112416,"like":221,"dislike":1,"score":220,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:40:27.000Z","msg":"既然林鄭月娥、李家超同盧偉聰都已經澄清左唔係佢地嘅決定，咁市民一定要向前線執勤警員追究到底，要佢地每一個都企出嚟承擔返個責任！"},{"pid":"107d1c1bcfffc2c86ab2508aa38222d5a6a2faf4","tid":1242503,"uid":18959,"like":229,"dislike":0,"score":229,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:42:22.000Z","msg":"香港最高職位唔認<br />\n黑警最大粒果個又唔攬上身<br />\n保安局都割埋<br />\n<br />\n點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7f6d25c1548dc6619330167f6a6e3446f90ff2","ti